<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span>وَيَغْتَسِلُ بِخَمْسِ مَكَاكِيَّ».<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>